        <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-num">11</div><div><div class="faq-q">How does office-based anesthesia + hybrid W-2 / 1099 qualify?</div><div class="faq-a">Hybrid W-2 + 1099 office-based CRNAs synthesize: W-2 component under B3-3.1-01 + 1099 component under B3-3.2-01 with Schedule C / 1120-S + Form 1084 add-backs. Multiple practice contracts documented separately. Common for dental anesthesia + plastic surgery + GI sedation CRNAs.</div></div></div>
